div1.p: United States of America, Western District of Washington } ss:

I hereby certify that I served the annexed Writ of Habeas Corpus on the therein-named Ellis DeBruler by handing to and leaving a true and correct copy thereof with Ellis DeBruler personally at Seattle in said District on the 16th day of April, A.D. 1913
div1.ab: Josephy R. M. Jacoby, U.S. Marshal
div1.p: In the District Court of the United States for the Western District of Washington Northern Divsion
In the Matter of the Application for Marie Miler for Writ of Habeas Corpus
Filed in the U.S. District Court, Western Dist. of Washington Apr 17 1913 Frank L. Crosby, Clerk.
Elias A. Wright Attorney for Petitioner 629 Burke Building Seattle Branch
